<section xml:id="yar.configuration" xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
 &reftitle.runtime;
 &extension.runtime;
 <para>
  <table>
   <title>Yar &ConfigureOptions;</title>
   <tgroup cols="4">
    <thead>
     <row>
      <entry>&Name;</entry>
      <entry>&Default;</entry>
      <entry>&Changeable;</entry>
      <entry>&Changelog;</entry>
     </row>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
     <row>
      <entry><link linkend="ini.yar.packager">yar.packager</link></entry>
      <entry>php</entry>
      <entry>PHP_INI_SYSTEM</entry>
      <entry><!-- leave empty, this will be filled by an automatic script --></entry>
     </row>
     <row>
      <entry><link linkend="ini.yar.debug">yar.debug</link></entry>
      <entry>Off</entry>
      <entry>PHP_INI_ALL</entry>
      <entry><!-- leave empty, this will be filled by an automatic script --></entry>
     </row>
     <row>
      <entry><link linkend="ini.yar.connect-timeout">yar.connect_timeout</link></entry>
      <entry>1000</entry>
      <entry>PHP_INI_ALL</entry>
      <entry><!-- leave empty, this will be filled by an automatic script --></entry>
     </row>
     <row>
      <entry><link linkend="ini.yar.timeout">yar.timeout</link></entry>
      <entry>5000</entry>
      <entry>PHP_INI_ALL</entry>
      <entry><!-- leave empty, this will be filled by an automatic script --></entry>
     </row>
     <row>
      <entry><link linkend="ini.yar.expose-info">yar.expose_info</link></entry>
      <entry>On</entry>
      <entry>PHP_INI_SYSTEM</entry>
      <entry><!-- leave empty, this will be filled by an automatic script --></entry>
     </row>
    </tbody>
   </tgroup>
  </table>
 </para>

 &ini.descriptions.title;

 <para>
  <variablelist>
   <varlistentry xml:id="ini.yar.packager">
     <term>
      <parameter>yar.packager</parameter>
      <type>string</type>
     </term>
     <listitem>
      <para>
       设置Yar的打包工具, 可以是PHP(serialize), JSON,
       Msgpack(这个需要编译的时候指定--enable-msgpack).
      </para>
     </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry xml:id="ini.yar.debug">
     <term>
      <parameter>yar.debug</parameter>
      <type>string</type>
     </term>
     <listitem>
      <para>
       打开的时候, Yar会把请求过程的日志都打印出来(到stderr).
      </para>
     </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry xml:id="ini.yar.connect-timeout">
     <term>
      <parameter>yar.connect_timeout</parameter>
      <type>int</type>
     </term>
     <listitem>
      <para>
       连接超时(毫秒为单位)
      </para>
     </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry xml:id="ini.yar.timeout">
     <term>
      <parameter>yar.timeout</parameter>
      <type>int</type>
     </term>
     <listitem>
      <para>
       处理超时(毫秒为单位)
      </para>
     </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry xml:id="ini.yar.expose-info">
     <term>
      <parameter>yar.expose_info</parameter>
      <type>bool</type>
     </term>
     <listitem>
      <para>
       如果关闭, 则当通过浏览器访问Server的时候, 不会出现Server Info信息.
      </para>
     </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

  </variablelist>
 </para>
</section>

